title: Massive Addons for Visual Composer v2.0 - Wordpress Plugin
description:
At the beginning we have investigated what is wrong with current addon packages and VC itself. Most of the packages are slow, heavy weight and does not look good. Each time you want to change something you need to go through tons of settings to achieve the same look. There is no easy way to easily create stuff with few clicks and that got us thinking.
 
http://codecanyon.net/item/massive-addons-uber-visual-composer-extension/14429839
